#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:8
msgid "Migrating to v1.0"
msgstr "遷移至 v1.0"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:10
msgid ""
"v1.0 is one of the biggest breaking changes in the library due to a complete "
"redesign."
msgstr "v1.0 是此程式庫中最大的破壞性變更之一，因為進行了完全的重新設計。"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:13
msgid ""
"The amount of changes are so massive and long that for all intents and "
"purposes, it is a completely new library."
msgstr "變更幅度如此之大，以至於實際上它是一個全新的程式庫。"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:16
msgid ""
"Part of the redesign involves making things more easy to use and natural. "
"Things are done on the :ref:`models <discord_api_models>` instead of "
"requiring a :class:`Client` instance to do any work."
msgstr ""
"重新設計的一部分是讓使用上更簡單、更自然。操作現在直接在 :ref:`模型 "
"<discord_api_models>` 上進行，而不需要:class:`Client` 實例來完成工作。"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:20
msgid "Python Version Change"
msgstr "Python 版本變更"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:22
msgid ""
"In order to make development easier and also to allow for our dependencies "
"to upgrade to allow usage of 3.7 or higher, the library had to remove "
"support for Python versions lower than 3.5.3, which essentially means that "
"**support for Python 3.4 is dropped**."
msgstr ""
"為了簡化開發並允許依賴項目升級以支援 3.7 或更高版本，此程式庫不得不移除對低"
"於 3.5.3 的 Python版本支援，這基本上意味著**已停止支援 Python 3.4**。"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:27
msgid "Major Model Changes"
msgstr "主要模型變更"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:29
msgid "Below are major model changes that have happened in v1.0"
msgstr "以下是 v1.0 中發生的主要模型變更"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:32
msgid "Snowflakes are int"
msgstr "Snowflake 改為 int"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:34
msgid ""
"Before v1.0, all snowflakes (the ``id`` attribute) were strings. This has "
"been changed to :class:`int`."
msgstr ""
"在 v1.0 之前，所有 snowflake（``id`` 屬性）都是字串。現已變更為 :class:"
"`int`。"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:36 ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:256
msgid "Quick example: ::"
msgstr "快速範例： ::"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:38
msgid ""
"# before\n"
"ch = client.get_channel('84319995256905728')\n"
"if message.author.id == '80528701850124288':\n"
"    ...\n"
"\n"
"# after\n"
"ch = client.get_channel(84319995256905728)\n"
"if message.author.id == 80528701850124288:\n"
"    ..."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:48
msgid ""
"This change allows for fewer errors when using the Copy ID feature in the "
"official client since you no longer have to wrap it in quotes and allows for "
"optimisation opportunities by allowing ETF to be used instead of JSON "
"internally."
msgstr ""
"此變更可減少使用官方客戶端中的「複製 ID」功能時的錯誤，因為您不再需要用引號括"
"起來，並且允許內部使用 ETF 而非 JSON來進行效能最佳化。"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:52
msgid "Server is now Guild"
msgstr "Server 改為 Guild"

#: ../../../migrating_to_v1.rst:54
msgid ""
"The official API documentation calls the \"Server\" concept a \"Guild\" "
"instead. In order to be more consistent with the API documentation when "
"necessary, the model has been renamed to :class:`Guild` and all instances "
"referring to it has been changed as well."
msgstr ""

